** Estructuras.
DATA: BEGIN OF R_ESTRUCTURA,
  CLAVE TYPE CHAR2,
  VENDOR_NO	TYPE LIFNR,
  AMT_DOCCUR TYPE	BAPIWRBTR,
  SP_GL_IND	TYPE ACPI_UMSKZ,
  VALUE_DATE TYPE	VALUT,
  ITEM_TEXT	TYPE SGTXT,
  COND_TYPE TYPE KSCHA,
  DIVISION TYPE SPART,
  RES_DOC	TYPE KBLNR,
  RES_ITEM TYPE KBLPOS,
  COSTCENTER TYPE KOSTL,
  FUND  TYPE BP_GEBER,
  FUNDS_CTR TYPE  FISTL,
  CMMT_ITEM	TYPE FIPOS,
  FUNC_AREA	TYPE FKBER_SHORT,
  WBS_ELEMENT TYPE PS_POSID,
END OF R_ESTRUCTURA.

** Tablas Internas.
DATA: TI_ESTRUCTURA LIKE R_ESTRUCTURA OCCURS 0 WITH HEADER LINE.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK BL01 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-000.
  PARAMETERS: P_BLDAT TYPE BLDAT OBLIGATORY,
              P_BUKRS TYPE BUKRS OBLIGATORY,
              P_BLART TYPE BLART OBLIGATORY,
              P_BUDAT TYPE BUDAT OBLIGATORY,
              P_WAERS TYPE WAERS OBLIGATORY,
              P_XBLNR TYPE XBLNR OBLIGATORY.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK BL01.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK BL02 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-001.
  PARAMETERS: P_FILE LIKE RLGRAP-FILENAME DEFAULT 'C:\' OBLIGATORY.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK BL02.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK BL03 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-002.
  PARAMETERS: P_REAL AS CHECKBOX.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK BL03.

** VALIDACIÓN DE CONTROL DE SELECCIÓN DE ARCHIVOS.
AT SELECTION-SCREEN ON VALUE-REQUEST FOR P_FILE.
  PERFORM SELECCIONAR_RUTA.
